        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 2. — A, Discradisca sp., South Madagascar, Bay of Galions, ATIMO VATAE, stn TP03, 17-21 m, dorsal view of complete specimen (IB-2013-28). B, C, Novocrania roseoradiata (Jackson, 1952), outer and inner views of dorsal valve (IB-2013-29), South Madagascar, S. Bay of Lokaro, ATIMO VATAE, stn TS09, 5-6 m. D-H, Novocrania sp., Mozambique Channel, Almirante Leite Bank, MAINBAZA, stn CC 3167, 228-230 m, dorsal valves (IB-2013-30-31); D, E, outer and inner views; F-H, inner view, and enlargement of posterior part to show muscle scars (G) and margin (H). A, D-H, SEM. Scale bars: A, 1 mm; B-G, 2 mm; H, 200 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4578156/files/figure.png" .

